{"tid":2019413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（世界大戰）諾蘭新作《TENET 天能》故事情節首度曝光！涉及「量子力學」、「時空扭曲」","createTime":"2020-05-16T09:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T10:44:47.000Z","uid":98659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9810c96fc69586474ac07cce4dd72d3f84c175d","tid":2019413,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:11:17.000Z","msg":"眾所期待的克里斯多夫諾蘭 Christopher Nolan 新作《TENET 天能》被譽為將與《全面啟動 Inception》齊名的燒腦科幻電影，尤其《天能》還選在跟 10 年前《全面啟動》上映的同一個日期上映，也不禁讓人猜想兩部作品的關係！而雖然《天能》已經發布電影預告，官方也說了這部電影故事將描述「一名秘密特工接到任務，以時間旅行的方式來阻止第三次世界大戰的發生」，但是真正的故事情節還是讓人摸不著頭緒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n不過現在在亞馬遜 Amazon 竟然上架了一本名為《天能的秘密：諾蘭的量子冷戰解密》（The Secrets of Tenet: Inside Christopher Nolan&rsquo;s Quantum Cold War）的精裝電影書籍，這本書的消息一出來就得到了熱烈的討論，也揭開了《天能》所提到的時間旅行概念是跟「量子力學」有關，同時可能也會牽扯到「時空扭曲」跟「平行時空」的問題。<br />\n<br />\n量子理論最先是由德國物理學家馬克斯普朗克 Max Planck 在 1900 年所提出，一開始是為了解釋在「任意溫度」下從「黑體」（在 1862 年被提出，一個夠吸收外來全部電磁輻射，並且不會有任何反射與透射的「理想化物體」）中發射出的「電磁輻射」的「輻射率」與「頻率」之間的關係；這個概念讓普朗克獲得了 1918 年的諾貝爾獎，不過當時普朗克認為「量子化」純粹只是一種「數學把戲」，殊不知這卻改變了我們對世界理解的基本原理&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n《天能》的故事將圍繞在對「未來」（但同時也是「過去」）的想像中，根據外媒的猜測，這可能涉指了主角必須回到過去阻止一場已經被阻止的核戰，牽扯到複雜的時間線，這可能比諾蘭的《記憶拼圖》、《全面啟動》還要燒腦，而同樣的主題也讓人聯想可能會是類似於電玩遊戲《量子裂痕 Quantum Break》的概念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/article/%E8%AB%BE%E8%98%AD-tenet-%E5%A4%A9%E8%83%BD-%E9%87%8F%E5%AD%90%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com.tw%2Fentertainment%2Farticle%2F%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%2598%25AD-tenet-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%2583%25BD-%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=85e88b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/article/%E8%AB%BE%E8%98%AD-tenet-%E5%A4%A9%E8%83%BD-%E9%87%8F%E5%AD%90%E5%8A%9B%E5%AD%B8</a>"},{"pid":"88e6ec327519f40abf1159a790c30aa14c6f33a5","tid":2019413,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"希治閣之後的緊張大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b44c9c1648cde40bb4e38b4d4de3ed2f91f3153","tid":2019413,"uid":165361,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"千其唔好同女人睇, 一定問東問西"},{"pid":"e97206f5a3a09a6b7a2b7d8538bd3c07e15dd77e","tid":2019413,"uid":217187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"幾時上"},{"pid":"f899596a39e210975c735e6ce440dfeefdd9193d","tid":2019413,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e97206f5a3a09a6b7a2b7d8538bd3c07e15dd77e","tid":2019413,"uid":217187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"幾時上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"7月16 日"},{"pid":"957f37a6bd6c081e45cfb2500e7463e351b641a3","tid":2019413,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/vbzxNDZMgiyqjoC6wesoZ5EdQtcYQBRN2j1LqtagAEqXFZI-mwUr73vGf8ysMux5nS4fKrsNlOYx6BIJt9THfePTRaitfAJUKK6PkE6G8b0VKromOFyVfMEF7rwuXTDoP8C3MY1VaSlRIAm9auhSfMg-iaNQ83SI27Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FvbzxNDZMgiyqjoC6wesoZ5EdQtcYQBRN2j1LqtagAEqXFZI-mwUr73vGf8ysMux5nS4fKrsNlOYx6BIJt9THfePTRaitfAJUKK6PkE6G8b0VKromOFyVfMEF7rwuXTDoP8C3MY1VaSlRIAm9auhSfMg-iaNQ83SI27Q&h=664a4b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}